parameters: So there's a place like this, huh?
T-That... isn't it as childhood friends, right...?
...I see... So that's how it was.
Because I've liked you for a long time...!!!
...W-What should I do in moments like this?

Ahaha... It's my first time, so I don't understand
anything...
...Ahaha... Well then... Shall we go home?

I intertwined my right hand with Aki's slender, soft, and
delicate fingertips as we made our way home.
Before we knew it, summer vacation was over.
It has been a few years since I started dating Aki...
